        <updateDate>2021-01-15T19:57:45Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>American Right to Vote Act</b></p> <p>This bill generally prohibits states from imposing additional conditions or requirements on the eligibility of individuals to cast ballots by mail in federal elections. It also requires the U.S. Postal Service to categorize, handle, and deliver election mail as first-class mail.</p> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
