        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Help America Vote Act of 2002 to prohibit States from imposing any additional conditions or requirements on the eligibility of individuals to cast votes in elections for Federal office by absentee ballot by mail, and for other purposes.</title>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
